{
  "stem": "16473.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 409.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And she, being a very strong-headed woman, decided she would admit it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And of course, they wouldn't let her come out to America.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So it was my father and I who could come out, and she had to stay behind.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "When she stayed behind, she, because she wasn't really a communist, she had to fend for herself.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And what she did is she had a live-in-- a live-in-- moving kindergarten.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "She picked up children all along the route between Buda and Pest, and then they went up to the mountains, rain or shine, and then she brought the kids back.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And so she indeed was not a communist.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Had she been one, she could have worked for the communist kindergarten system.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So in any case, she was left behind.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Everybody was very excited about us coming.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And father's friend, who was a writer, wrote me a poem that I have in my autograph book.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And when the time came to leave, it's very interesting.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I only have this memory a couple of years ago.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We went by train from Hungary to Vienna, and mother standing on the platform and she's crying.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And before we left, I'm comforting her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Soon, you'll be with us, you'll be with us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And as the train is moving out of the platform, the thought comes to me, I'm leaving you now.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So I know that that abandonment was just a big issue.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I know it from later life, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But anyway, so I remember that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But when we arrived in New York with my uncle, who made it from Czechoslovakia-- they went to Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "They went there and within a few months they could come here.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
